FuncDef: This command overrides the scheduling rate applied to the HS WRR group as a percentage of the port rate, including both the port's egress rate and port's HS scheduler policy maximum rate, if configured. The override rate type must match the corresponding rate type within the applied QoS policy.

ParaDef.Info: Specifies the percent rate of the HS WRR group. Values-0.01 to 100.00.
